{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778987309499,"sessionID":"ses_1cc17fd5bffeQIGMKJLRwjtTA3","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_KXnwFTKp0IE0Zcn8C5D4lsBn","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/__issue_context__.json","offset":1,"limit":400},"output":"<path>/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/__issue_context__.json</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: {\n2:   \"body\": \"**GO:XXX; venom-mediated activation of inflammatory response**\\nSyn: Venom-mediated inflammation (BROAD)\\nA process by which an organism causes inflammatory response in another organism via the action of a venom. Venom-mediated inflammation is related to edema, leucocyte infiltration and release of inflammatory mediators such as cytokines.\\nPMID:32024243, PMID:19000915\\n**Gene product name and ID to be annotated to this term**\\nMany snake venom metalloproteinases (eg. A0A0K2JNB8, P85420 or P0DRN9)\\n**Parent term(s)**\\nGO:0035738; venom-mediated perturbation of biological process\\n**Children terms**\\nGO:0044398; venom-mediated edema\\n\\n\\n\\n**GO:XXX; Venom-mediated leukocyte infiltration**\\nA process by which an organism causes leucocyte infiltration in another organism via the action of a venom.\\nPMID:32024243, PMID:26072684, PMID:19000915\\n**Gene product name and ID to be annotated to this term**\\nMany snake venom metalloproteinases (eg. A0A0K2JNB8, P85420, P0DRO0)\\n**Parent term(s)**\\nGO:XXX; Venom-mediated inflammatory response\\n\\n\\n\\n**GO:XXX; Venom-mediated release of inflammatory mediator**\\nSyn: venom-mediated production of proinflammatory mediator\\nA process by which an organism causes release of inflammatory mediator in another organism via the action of a venom. Inflammatory mediator is possibly a cytokines or interleukins, for example.\\nPMID:32024243, 26072684\\n**Gene product name and ID to be annotated to this term**\\nMany snake venom metalloproteinases (eg. A0A0K2JNB8, P0DRO0)\\n**Parent term(s)**\\nGO:XXX; Venom-mediated inflammatory response\\n\\n\\n\\n**GO:0044480; venom-mediated mast cell degranulation**\\nTo add:\\nPart_of : GO:XXX; Venom-mediated inflammatory response\",\n3:   \"comments\": [\n4:     {\n5:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws8AAAABBfg_CA\",\n6:       \"author\": {\n7:         \"login\": \"pgaudet\"\n8:       },\n9:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n10:       \"body\": \"@dragon-ai-agent please add this new term: \\n\\n- venom-mediated activation of inflammatory response\\n- Synonym: venom-mediated inflammation (BROAD)\\n- Definition: A process by which an organism causes inflammatory response in another organism via the action of a venom. \\n- References: PMID:32024243, PMID:19000915\\n- Subclass of: GO:0035738; venom-mediated perturbation of biological process\\n\",\n11:       \"createdAt\": \"2026-05-07T07:37:31Z\",\n12:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n13:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n14:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n15:       \"reactionGroups\": [\n16:         {\n17:           \"content\": \"EYES\",\n18:           \"users\": {\n19:             \"totalCount\": 1\n20:           }\n21:         }\n22:       ],\n23:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31902#issuecomment-4395122440\",\n24:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n25:     },\n26:     {\n27:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws8AAAABBfhJ9A\",\n28:       \"author\": {\n29:         \"login\": \"dragon-ai-agent\"\n30:       },\n31:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n32:       \"body\": \"🤖 Working on it...\\n\\nFollow along: [View workflow run](https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/actions/runs/25482614504)\\n\\n*— @dragon-ai-agent*\",\n33:       \"createdAt\": \"2026-05-07T07:37:59Z\",\n34:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n35:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n36:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n37:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n38:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31902#issuecomment-4395125236\",\n39:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n40:     }\n41:   ],\n42:   \"title\": \"NTR: [venom-mediated inflammatory response+... leukocyte infiltration+... release of inflammatory mediator]\",\n43:   \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31902\"\n44: }\n\n(End of file - total 44 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"{\n  \"body\": \"**GO:XXX; venom-mediated activation of inflammatory response**\\nSyn: Venom-mediated inflammation (BROAD)\\nA process by which an organism causes inflammatory response in another organism via the action of a venom. Venom-mediated inflammation is related to edema, leucocyte infiltration and release of inflammatory mediators such as cytokines.\\nPMID:32024243, PMID:19000915\\n**Gene product name and ID to be annotated to this term**\\nMany snake venom metalloproteinases (eg. A0A0K2JNB8, P85420 or P0DRN9)\\n**Parent term(s)**\\nGO:0035738; venom-mediated perturbation of biological process\\n**Children terms**\\nGO:0044398; venom-mediated edema\\n\\n\\n\\n**GO:XXX; Venom-mediated leukocyte infiltration**\\nA process by which an organism causes leucocyte infiltration in another organism via the action of a venom.\\nPMID:32024243, PMID:26072684, PMID:19000915\\n**Gene product name and ID to be annotated to this term**\\nMany snake venom metalloproteinases (eg. A0A0K2JNB8, P85420, P0DRO0)\\n**Parent term(s)**\\nGO:XXX; Venom-mediated inflammatory response\\n\\n\\n\\n**GO:XXX; Venom-mediated release of inflammatory mediator**\\nSyn: venom-mediated production of proinflammatory mediator\\nA process by which an organism causes release of inflammatory mediator in another organism via the action of a venom. Inflammatory mediator is possibly a cytokines or interleukins, for example.\\nPMID:32024243, 26072684\\n**Gene product name and ID to be annotated to this term**\\nMany snake venom metalloproteinases (eg. A0A0K2JNB8, P0DRO0)\\n**Parent term(s)**\\nGO:XXX; Venom-mediated inflammatory response\\n\\n\\n\\n**GO:0044480; venom-mediated mast cell degranulation**\\nTo add:\\nPart_of : GO:XXX; Venom-mediated inflammatory response\",\n  \"comments\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws8AAAABBfg_CA\",\n      \"author\": {\n        \"login\": \"pgaudet\"\n      },\n      \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n      \"body\": \"@dragon-ai-agent please add this new term: \\n\\n- venom-mediated activation of inflammatory response\\n- Synonym: venom-mediated inflammation (BROAD)\\n- Definition: A process by which an organism causes inflammatory response in another organism via the action of a venom. \\n- References: PMID:32024243, PMID:19000915\\n- Subclass of: GO:0035738; venom-mediated perturbation of biological process\\n\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-05-07T07:37:31Z\",\n      \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n      \"isMinimized\": false,\n      \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n      \"reactionGroups\": [\n        {\n          \"content\": \"EYES\",\n          \"users\": {\n            \"totalCount\": 1\n          }","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"__issue_context__.json","time":{"start":1778987309436,"end":1778987309497}},"id":"prt_e33e8196f001tCncxFtiLm1s1g","sessionID":"ses_1cc17fd5bffeQIGMKJLRwjtTA3","messageID":"msg_e33e803cb001AqSd1hvTSYEkgh"}}
