{"type":"text","timestamp":1778987488678,"sessionID":"ses_1cc17fd5bffeQIGMKJLRwjtTA3","part":{"id":"prt_e33eac5d3001xwEr0nF9Te6lkO","messageID":"msg_e33ea7aa8001mzyKqmbhUsKWWc","sessionID":"ses_1cc17fd5bffeQIGMKJLRwjtTA3","type":"text","text":"I found one important ontology nuance: `venom-mediated edema` is better connected as `part_of` the new inflammatory-response term, not as an `is_a` child. I’m checking out the affected existing terms and creating a small new-term batch file so the final structure matches the issue’s requested parent/child semantics without overstating equivalence.","time":{"start":1778987484627,"end":1778987488676}}}
